1. *Braku* je pokazao ljubav i večnu predanost. (He showed love and eternal dedication to the marriage.). 
2. Ona je bila u potpunom *braku* sa svojim mužem. (She was in a complete marriage with her husband.) 
3. Njih dvoje su objavili *brak* pre nekoliko meseci. (The two of them announced their marriage a few months ago.) 
4. Oni su ušli u *brak* iz čistog prijateljstva. (They entered the marriage out of pure friendship.) 
5. Ona se nije želela udati za njega, ali je njen otac naterao *brak*. (She didn't want to marry him, but her father forced the marriage.)